    <title>Credits</title>
    <para>
In producing this document, I have gathered information from the Freevo mailing list, the Freevo documentation and the MPlayer documentation. Without these two projects my dream of creating a Linux based PVR and the creation of this document would not be possible.
    </para>
  </sect1>

